Quick type fix in the API client.

```diff
// src/services/api-client.ts
- export async function fetchUsers(): Promise<any> {
+ export async function fetchUsers(): Promise<ApiResponse<User[]>> {
    const response = await axios.get('/api/users');
    return response.data;
  }
```

Was using `any` as a placeholder when we first wrote this. Now that the `ApiResponse` type exists, swapped it in. No behavior change, just type safety.

